title: PICS: 7 Miss South Africa winners as toddlers and tweens
text:
PICS: 7 Miss South Africa winners as toddlers and tweens share this

Cape Town - From Rolene Strauss and Tamaryn Green to Basetsana Kumalo, we take a look at how seven former Miss South Africas looked as children.

Taken before the "selfie" and the digital camera, these beauties were captured on film.

So, if you've ever wondered what Cindy Nell and Demi-Leigh Nel-Peters looked like before they were crowned, wonder no more!

We love an early throwback - here are some of our favourites.

ALSO READ: WATCH: It's official, Sasha-Lee Olivier is heading to London for Miss World

Spoiler alert: Some of the beauty queens haven't changed a bit!

1. Rolene Strauss (Miss South Africa 2014, Miss World 2014)

2. Demi-Leigh Nel-Peters (Miss South Africa 2017, Miss Universe 2017)

3. Tamaryn Green (Miss South Africa 2018)

4. Basetsana Kumalo

5. Cindy Nell-Roberts (Miss South Africa 2002)

6. Ntandoyenkosi Kunene (Miss South Africa 2016)

7. Bokang Montjane-Tshabalala (Miss South Africa (2010)

Compiled by Graye Morkel
